trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9DocumentDescription class defines the description of the content of a CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: Klassen Pkcs9DocumentDescription definerer beskrivelsen av innholdet i en CMS/PKCS #7-melding.

trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9DocumentDescription constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentDescription"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren Pkcs9DocumentDescription oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentDescription"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9DocumentDescription constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentDescription"></xref> class by using the specified array of byte values as the encoded description of the content of a CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren Pkcs9DocumentDescription oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentDescription"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av den angitte matrisen byte som kodet beskrivelsen av innholdet i en CMS/PKCS #7-melding.

trans-unit.source: An array of byte values that specifies the encoded description of the CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: En matrise med byteverdier som angir kodet beskrivelsen av CMS/PKCS #7-melding.

trans-unit.source: The Pkcs9DocumentDescription constructor creates an instance of the <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentDescription"></xref> class by using the specified description of the content of a CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: Konstruktøren Pkcs9DocumentDescription oppretter en forekomst av den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentDescription"> </xref> klassen ved hjelp av den angitte beskrivelsen av innholdet i en CMS/PKCS #7-melding.

trans-unit.source: An instance of the <xref:System.String> class that specifies the description for the CMS/PKCS #7 message.
trans-unit.target: En forekomst av den <xref:System.String>klasse som angir beskrivelsen for CMS/PKCS #7-melding.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: This method replaces the current <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentDescription> object with the specified <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData> object.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden erstatter gjeldende <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentDescription>objekt med angitt <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData>objektet.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.Pkcs9DocumentDescription>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData"></xref> object from which to copy information.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Security.Cryptography.AsnEncodedData"> </xref> objektet vil kopiere informasjon fra.

trans-unit.source: The DocumentDescription property retrieves the document description.
A <xref:System.String> object that contains the document description.
